reviewText: Vintage erotic films are interesting and often surprising.  But - this set may be that, but the transfer to DVD is so bad that you can't really tell what is going on.  Apparently the original transfer was made from copies of copies and with no cleaning up or enhancing of the film they had available
Interesting videos from before my time.  Quality isn't great, but that is expected.  Overall a good collection, I would recommend it if you're into these old films.
not like most other vintage movies
Not what I expected, but it's something different
Old classic movies. Good for historical value only.
